snippet.title: Colin McRae Rally 2005 Plus PSP Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Colin McRae Rally 2005 Plus PSP Gameplay HD.

Colin McRae Rally 2005 is a racing video game developed and published by Codemasters for PlayStation 2, Xbox, Microsoft Windows, N-Gage, Mobile, PlayStation Portable and OS X. It is the fifth game in the Colin McRae Rally series.
